column5: Hey Gang,  Here are some pics of our last outing. The fishing was awesome as always! I brought out my good friends brother for his second time and he nailed a monster (14.4). We didn"t get the numbers that we usually do but all the fish caught were over 6 lbs. All fish were released.... Heading up on Friday for the last dance with mother Walleye... I hope there will be lots of pics to post....
Wow...nice fish...!!!  How did your trip on GB go last month?
Freezing and almost killed myself and DMASSE. Wiped out pretty hard with the car in the middle of a SERIOUS snow storm. Thank the Good Lord we didn"t go into the ditch! Landed on eye about 6 inches!
Grant, nice bumping into you at Bass Pro today!!!  I hope you found that lucky lure   Good luck with your last trip to BOQ.  When you get back we'll have to hit Lake Ontario for some 'Urban fishing'
Nice eyes grant good luck on your next trip  rob
Good goin Grant! Nice chunks there!
Some real good lookin fish  ..WTG  Grant...
Very nice Grant and to think we missed out on fishin with you last November I have a spot for you in the boat if you bring that big horshoe that is stuffed .........................
